title: Bug 116609[Regression] Color orange doesn't work.
description: Bug 116609[Regression] Color orange doesn't work. Description: The color orange is not being applied correctly. Steps to reproduce: 1. Insert a report item. 2. Set the color or background color to orange.
OB: When previewing the report, the orange color does not appear as expected.
EB: The orange color should be applied correctly to the report item when previewing the report.
SR: 1. Insert a report item. 2. Set the color or background color to orange. 3. Preview the report to see if the orange color is applied correctly.
